Harry Reems stars as Dr. Schmock, a zany mad scientist who accidentally discovers Preparation X. It's a formula that can make an ordinary meatball swell two twice it's normal size. 
But whenever a guy eats it, it also has a similar effect on him! 
The good doctor tests out his creation and ends up with a constant erection that even his sexiest assistants can't calm down. 
Filled with 70's superstars like Tina Russell and Andrea True.
